Package: LocalHierarchy
Type: Package
Title: Flexible set up for hierarchical modeling and local fitting
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: c(person("Herbert", "Susmann", email = "herbps10@gmail.com", role = c("aut")),
              person("Evan", "Ray", role = c("aut")),
             person("Leontine", "Alkema", email = "lalkema@umass.edu", role = c("aut", "cre")))
Description: The LocalHierarchy package implements a flexible set up to estimate parameters hierarchically 
    and to carry out local model fits, whereby higher-level parameters are fixed. The hierarchical set up is taken from BayesTransitionModels. 
